{"tid":434004,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發有圖) 痴漢地鐵露鳩非禮ol","createTime":"2017-10-13T01:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T05:29:56.000Z","uid":19194,"like":11,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"39531146f37dcc3a19da06db3ad01c999a91e75f","tid":434004,"uid":19194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:23:17.000Z","msg":"頭先喺將軍澳線，返工時間好迫，我前面就企左個ol, 10點鐘方向係個痴漢<br />\n<br />\n痴漢著灰t,件t 好長，我見佢一路蚊著件T，個行為都好奇怪，所以一路有留意著佢，佢愈行愈前，用j貼著個ol pat pat，磨左幾下，睇真啲，我屌，竟然係露撚左條j 出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，見到嗰下真係呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等車門合返埋既時候，我拍ol 膊頭同佢講返件事（嗰陣痴漢仲喺車上面），但佢都冇回應我，聽完之後淨係吓左一聲。。事主都唔冇諗著有進一步行動，我都做唔到啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以唯有大家認著佢，叫身邊女仔自己小心啲，人多啲時候要保護好自己，痴漢大約17x cm，中等身型，3x 歲左右<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/091754_0f7b2c2873907a4ffe4b83139360f036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F091754_0f7b2c2873907a4ffe4b83139360f036.jpg&h=c9265def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/091908_e1c3e04d9cffdbe5ca65239c5d06518d.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F091908_e1c3e04d9cffdbe5ca65239c5d06518d.jpg&d=OsW8RhCjDOjl8urPPrlWSV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=940c169e\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/091908_e1c3e04d9cffdbe5ca65239c5d06518d.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"12b299b00c2f916ceaa11679f4265093c7e19852","tid":434004,"uid":63952,"like":159,"dislike":1,"score":158,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:28:48.000Z","msg":"搵左幾秒先搵到碌鳩喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64c5e5991ca85252afc40a5741a3cad1f88e38c","tid":434004,"uid":28195,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10